'From Cuis 1.0 of 21 May 2009 [latest update: #204] on 18 June 2009 at 7:37:52 pm'!"Change Set:		nilMNU-bfDate:			17 June 2009Author:			Bert FreudenbergIf the receiver in a MessageNotUnderstood exception is nil, use a more informative description"!!MessageNotUnderstood methodsFor: 'exceptionBuilder' stamp: 'jmv 6/18/2009 19:37'!messageText	"Return an exception's message text."		^messageText == nil		ifTrue:			[message == nil				ifTrue: [super messageText]				ifFalse: [					message lookupClass == UndefinedObject						ifTrue: ['receiver of #{1} is nil' translated format: {message selector}]						ifFalse: [message lookupClass printString, '>>', message selector asString]]]		ifFalse: [messageText]! !